          "cachedResultName": "models/gemini-2.5-flash"
        },
        "text": "You are an expert data extraction AI. Analyze the attached receipt image and return the information ONLY as a valid, flat JSON object. No other text or markdown formatting outside the JSON is allowed.\n\n    Categorize the purchase into exactly ONE of the following predefined categories based on these descriptions:\n\n        Rent: Housing costs, rent notices, or fees directly related to accommodation.\n\n        Transport: Tickets for trains, buses, flights, taxis, fuel, parking, or bicycle rentals.\n\n        Groceries: Supermarkets, food stores, groceries (excluding restaurant visits).\n\n        Entertainment & Dining: Restaurant visits, cafes, bars, cinema, museums, events, and experiences.\n\n        Memberships: Subscriptions, gym memberships, software licenses, or recurring services.\n\n        Other: Anything that does not clearly fit into the above, or if the purpose of the receipt is unclear.\n\n    The JSON structure MUST look exactly like this:\n    {\n    \"category\": \"[Selected category from the list above]\",\n    \"amount\": [Numbers only, use a dot as a decimal separator],\n    \"currency\": \"[e.g., EUR or SEK]\",\n    \"merchant\": \"[Name of the store, merchant, or recipient]\",\n    \"date\": \"[YYYY-MM-DD]\"\n    }",
        "inputType": "binary",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.googleGemini",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [240, -192],
